    dcterms:source "Group type code 05"@en ;
    epr:status "Legacy"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote "GIAS group type 05. In the target EPR model, the sponsoring body is modelled as an epr:Organisation linked via epro:sponsoredBy on epr:Establishment. Sponsor is a role an organisation plays, not a type of establishment group."@en .

